|$. We also describe a special case of unit-grid square\nassemblies, where a connected partition can always be found in $O(n)$-time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Sep 2020 17:59:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Mar 2023 17:14:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-23"}
