 expected from grain-surface chemistry are also consistent\nwith our data. Further investigations of the ortho-to-para ratio in ND$_2$ ,\nboth theoretical and observational, could bring new constraints to better\nunderstand nitrogen hydride chemistry.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Sep 2020 18:00:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-29"}
